	"description":"The Associated Starline Parcels Syndicate began as a courier concern and grew into a commercial state through mergers, debts, favors, and quietly enforced contracts. Paddington sells the sector a polished logistics brand while the Familia keeps the criminal machinery running underneath. ASP fleets prefer deterrence, carriers, private security, and fast punitive violence over open conquest.",
